This example is from:
http://lammps.sandia.gov/tutorials/sor13/SoR_04-Hands_on_Simple_LAMMPS_Examples.pdf

Required input files are:

in.friction: from LAMMPS source code distributions. 

Basic commands are:

module swap PrgEnv-cray PrgEnv-gnu
module load fftw
module load cudatoolkit
module load lammps

lmp_xe6 < in.friction
